text: Humberto García may refer to: *Humberto Leal Garcia (1973–2011), Mexican criminal and inmate on death row in Texas *Humberto Tony García, American voice actor and announcer *Humberto García Reyes (born 1953), Mexican politician *Humberto García, manager of Club Sport Colombia *Humberto Garcia, guitar player on 4 (Kumbia Kings album)
title: Humberto García
